readable.content: A couple on the stairs are photographing a man and woman embracing in front of a building . A couple stands at the top of the stairs and two people stand at the bottom . A man and woman pose outside of a building while talking to two other people . A man and woman stand at the top of cement stairs together . A man holds a woman as another couple walk up the steps towards them .
